beer.beer_description: A collaboration between Stockade Brew Co and Mjølner inspired by a traditional Norse brew to quench the thirst of Odin himself. This beer has a  slight honey like flavour, coupled with citrus from the addition of orange peel and then juniper berries which add a tart, resinous and piney note. Ska!!
